# Global gitignore (Git's core.excludesfile, XDG default location).

# Claude Code records "don't ask again" permission approvals in
# .claude/settings.local.json, the per-machine personal settings file. Ignore
# it in every repo so personal permission state is never committed. Settings
# meant to be shared belong in .claude/settings.json, which is not ignored.
**/.claude/settings.local.json
